Requirements and dependencies:
Python 2.7
Skype4Py - get it from here: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Skype4Py/
Crypto (on windows machines only)

How to use:
Turn on your skype
Run the scrypt using "python consoleSkype.py"
Type "user:#{username_of_the_person_to_chat_with}"
Start sending your crypted messages...
Donate here: http://www.elsys-bg.org/ :)
